  <Docs>
    <summary>Provides extension methods for converting between <see cref="T:SkiaSharp.SKColor" />, <see cref="T:SkiaSharp.SKColorF" />, and <see cref="T:HarfBuzzSharp.HBColor" /> color types.</summary>
    <remarks><format type="text/markdown"><![CDATA[
## Remarks

These extension methods allow seamless conversion between SkiaSharp and HarfBuzzSharp color representations.

## Examples

```csharp
SKColor skColor = SKColors.Red;
HBColor hbColor = skColor.ToHBColor();
SKColor restored = hbColor.ToSKColor();
```
]]></format></remarks>
